    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a project with potential? This vehicle is ready for someone with a mechanical touch to bring it back to its former glory! It\u2019s in poor condition and will definitely need some TLC and repairs, but it offers a fantastic, low-cost opportunity for a DIY enthusiast or anyone looking for a budget-friendly fixer-upper. Grab this diamond in the rough and make it your own!",
